ps://api.github.com/users/ghajini","html_url":"https://github.com/ghajini","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ghajini/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ghajini/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ghajini/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ghajini/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ghajini/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ghajini/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ghajini/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ghajini/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ghajini/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"# Sorry. The website is infected by AdShield, Inc.\n\nUnfortunately, It is complicated to resolve with a regular adblock rule because the website is being protected by service of Ad-Shield that is an anti-adblock company.\n\n## Userscript Installation\nPlease block Ad-Shield advertisement by installing [tinyShield userscript](https://github.com/FilteringDev/tinyShield).\nPlease check its installation guideline written in English by visiting [this URL](https://github.com/FilteringDev/tinyShield/blob/main/README.md).\n\nIf you can understand Korean language, please refer https://github.com/FilteringDev/tinyShield/blob/main/README.ko.md.\n\n<details>\n<summary>Detailed description for iOS users</summary>\n\n1. Install [**Usercripts**](https://apps.apple.com/us/app/userscripts/id1463298887) app\n2. Enable **Usercripts** extension in Safari settings\n\t* iOS 18+: `System settings` => `Apps` => `Safari` => `Extensions`\n\t* iOS 17 and older: `System settings` => `Safari` => `Extensions`\n\tFind **Usercripts**, enable it and allow `On other sites` permission\n3. Open the [tinyShield ](https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@filteringdev/tinyshield@latest/dist/tinyShield.user.js) userscript URL in browser\n4. Press the extensions icon in the address bar of Safari and select Userscripts \n5. Tap to install\n6. In opened popup, scroll down and press Install button\n7. Done.\n\n</details>\n\n## Still Have a Problem?\nAn issue is occurred when the userscript is applied, please report to [this issue tracker](https://github.com/FilteringDev/tinyShield/issues).","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/226263/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/226263/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed","pinned_comment":null},"comment":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/comments/4020386748","html_url":"https://github.com/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/226263#issuecomment-4020386748","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/AdguardTeam/AdguardFilters/issues/226263","id":4020386748,"node_id":"IC_kwDOAVlsM87voju8","user":{"login":"WilliamCraft","id":165777412,"node_id":"U_kgDOCeGQBA","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/165777412?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/WilliamCraft","html_url":"https://github.com/WilliamCraft","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/WilliamCraft/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/WilliamCraft/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/WilliamCraft/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/WilliamCraft/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/WilliamCraft/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/WilliamCraft/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/WilliamCr